title: F1 2013 Barcelona Winter Test 2 Day 2.TBK
description:
Coverage of the Winter Testing Live from SKY SPORTS F1 HD. I do hope you enjoy my torrents, which im sure you appreciate, do take considerable time and effort. To reduce SKY's LIVE sync errors with audio during add-breaks. I have left the commercials intact as i've often mentioned before, that removing them can cause considerable encoding and playback problems as the live stream switches from Dolby Digital to standard stereo output during add breaks and then back, which plays havoc with encoding the feed as AC3 Digital.

To keep file sizes to a minimum, the video has been scaled from 1080p source down to 720p. High Profile 3.1 has been used to cut down on encoding times.

All torrents for F1 2013 will be encoded to MKV format with 720p resolution & AC3 Dolby Digital Audio. These video files should play smoothly with the standard media players such as VLC, WMP, KM Player, WMC, MP-HC.
